headline: How Much Upside is Left in Omnicom (OMC)? Wall Street Analysts Think 25.37%
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 25.4% in Omnicom (OMC). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
